channel.title: Need help with a few things please
channel.description:
#1, I made a new command in commands.java and it's not doing anything in the game. Do I have to compile it or somthing?? If so what do I need to do that.
#2, I really need the name of the file that contains items and the skills that you require to use them ect, prices and whatnot.. Like alot of things are wrong eg. Crystal bow can be used without 70 range..

item.title: Need help with a few things please
item.dc:creator: @Rich_Dude99 Rich Dude99
item.description:
@Rich_Dude99 wrote:

dimebagx:

#1, I made a new command in commands.java and it’s not doing anything in the game. Do I have to compile it or somthing?? If so what do I need to do that.

Yes… you must compile your server click compile.bat and compile your server!

dimebagx:

#2, I really need the name of the file that contains items and the skills that you require to use them ect, prices and whatnot… Like alot of things are wrong eg. Crystal bow can be used without 70 range…

That is more on the client side of coding, but you can do minor stages of that using shop coding and such…

-Hope this helps,
Rich Dude99
